name: Girls Code Club
body:
![Girls Code Club](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/girlscode/girlscode.github.io/master/gcc-logo.png)

Would you like to learn to make your own video games and computer animations? 

Then, this club is for you.

Learn the fundamentals of programming and computer science. 

Get inspired by your friends and by the great women in engineering that have changed the world with code.
